<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5813] Creating a SolrCore with a collection name of empty string should fail nicely in SolrCloud mode.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5813</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently it can cause a bit of havoc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12698747">SOLR-5813</key>
            <summary>Creating a SolrCore with a collection name of empty string should fail nicely in SolrCloud mode.</summary>
